Collecting user data helps us improve the game.\n\nPlayers who opt out of data communication will no longer send us crash reports and play data.\n\nThey will also be unable to receive new item unlocks from our servers, though existing unlocked items will continue to function.\n\nFor more details on our privacy policy and how we use the data we collect, please visit our <color=#ECA6C9><u><b>privacy center</b></u></color>.